    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es eſmu tas KUNGS/\nes runnaschu/ tas Wahrdṣ/ ko\nes runnaschu/ taps darrihtṣ/ we\ntaps wairṣ kawchts/ bet juhfu\nDeenâṣ af pahrgalwigṣ Namnṣ!\nrunnaschu es wecnu Wahrdσ/ un darrischu to/ fakka tas KUNGS\ntaṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wehl notikke ta KUNga\nteem Plaifuneein/ nedṣ dar-\nSehtu ap to Israêta Naimm\nun ne stahwat Karxâ ta KU-\nGA Deend.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tu Zilweka Behrnṣ/\nraugi/ tas Israêta Namnṣ fakka:\nTa Parabdiſchana/ ko wiꞥſch\nreds/ welkahṣ us ilgu Laiku/\nun wiꞥſch fluddina no Laikeim/\nkaṣ tahtu ur.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz fakkt us wiꞥ-\nReein : Ta fakka tas KUNGS\nKUNGS: Me tahdi no man-\nneem Wahrdem taps aisfawe-\nti/ tas Wahrdṣ/ ko es efmu ruu-\nnajṣ/ taps dar:ihtṣ/ fakka tas\nKUNge KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ca XIII. Nodalla.\nBahrya Gluddinaſchana tik labbi prett teem\nwiltigeem Praueeſcheem : 1/2. Kaṣ tohṣ\nDeewa Kaudis wilci i eeprezinaja un droh-\nschus darrija : 3. Ki:\ncriprett tahni wilti-\nsahm Praueetenchni : 17. Kas tecin Lau-\nbim Spilwenys appakſch Paduſſeem en\nGalwas darrija/ tas irr/ tohs Kaudis Jawôṣ\nGrekfôṣ weyl-apſtiprinaja : 14.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo ta KUNga Wahrdṣ\nteem notikke us man / kaṣ\ntoẓẓija:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tu Zilweka Behrns/\ndina prett Israêta Pra-\nſcheein/ kaṣ nahtoschas Le-\nfluddina/ un takki us teem/\nno fawa Prahta fluddina: Ki-\nfijt ta KUNGA Wahrdσ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta fakka tas Ku-\nKUNGS: Waj teem trak-\nBraueefscheem! kaṣ pehz fe-\nPrahta staiga/ un tomehr nie-\nka ne redṣ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tawi Praueefchi af J-\nel! irr ta Lapfas tukchaṣ W-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juhe ne zellatees pr-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winnσ Parabdiſchana\nweltiga un Mellu Stahſtifc-\nna. Tee fakka: Tas KUNG-\nicr to fazzijs/ kur tomehr t-\nKUNGS tohs ne irr fuhti-\nun tee leek ar Zerribu zerrecht/\nWahrdσ apſtiprinadami.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Woj ta ne irr weena a-\nlana Parabdiſchana/ un jut-\nfakkat Mellu Stahſtifchana-\ntoinehr fakkit juhs :\nKUNGS icr to runnajs / k-\nes ne efmu runnajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht ta fakka tas KUNG-\nKUNGS: Tapehz ka juhs a-\nlain ry-najat / un Mellu P-\nrahdiſchanas redsat/ tadeht ra-\ngt / ic grobu prett juhs/ fuu-\ntas KUNgs KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un manna Rohka turri-\ntees prett trem Praueefscheem\n"
